Way it goes is thus, Mob misses with its attack, spell will get off. <br>
Spell is in the last stage of casting, it will go off as the mob hits you. <br>
Sometimes, mob could be whacking the tar out of you and the spell goes off. I think it depends on your spec level in the skill, the type of spell cast and the amount of hit points the mob is at when the spell is cast.<br>
Mostly, you JUST have to hit that hot key button alot...heh.<br>
